## üìã Complete Deployment Checklist

### **For Python Distribution:**
- [ ] Test Python installation (`python --version`)
- [ ] Install required packages (`pip install pandas openpyxl`)
- [ ] Verify script runs (`python auditor_app1.py`)
- [ ] Create user documentation
- [ ] Test on clean machine

### **For Executable Distribution:**
- [ ] Install PyInstaller (`pip install pyinstaller`)
- [ ] Create executable (`pyinstaller --onefile --windowed auditor_app1.py`)
- [ ] Test .exe on target Windows machine
- [ ] Check antivirus compatibility
- [ ] Create installer package (optional)
- [ ] Prepare user guide
- [ ] Test installation process

### **For Enterprise Deployment:**
- [ ] Create MSI package
- [ ] Add to software distribution system
- [ ] Prepare admin installation guide
- [ ] Test with different Excel versions
- [ ] Verify with sample client data

